('eFISIO Carabanchel Usera', 'Physiotherapy', 'English-speaking physiotherapy clinic in the Carabanchel/Usera area of Madrid. Part of the eFISIO network with 25+ licensed physiotherapists across 6 clinics. Specializes in manual therapy, dry needling (punción seca), sports physiotherapy, traumatic rehabilitation, neurological physiotherapy, and pelvic floor therapy. Offers advanced treatments including shockwave therapy (ondas de choque), EPTE, EPI ultrasound-guided, and neuromodulation. Personalized 50-minute sessions with exclusive one-on-one attention. Online booking available with free initial phone consultation. Licensed by Colegio de Fisioterapeutas and authorized by Comunidad de Madrid.', 'Calle Portalegre, 77', 'Madrid', 'Madrid', '+34 910 052 363', 'contacto@efisio.es', 'https://www.efisio.es/clinica/fisioterapia-carabanchel/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- eFISIO Fisioterapia Getafe
('eFISIO Fisioterapia Getafe', 'Physiotherapy', 'English-speaking physiotherapy clinic serving Getafe and southern Madrid. Part of the eFISIO network with 25+ licensed physiotherapists. Comprehensive services include manual therapy, therapeutic massage (descontracturante, sports, relaxation, pregnancy), dry needling, and instrumental physiotherapy. Specialists in sports injury rehabilitation, post-surgical recovery, and chronic pain management. Advanced treatments: shockwave therapy, ultrasound-guided EPI, and neuromodulation. Licensed by Colegio de Fisioterapeutas and authorized by Comunidad de Madrid. Online booking with free initial consultation.', 'Calle Capitán Carlos Haya, 1', 'Getafe', 'Madrid', '+34 910 052 363', 'contacto@efisio.es', 'https://www.efisio.es/clinica/fisioterapia-getafe/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- eFISIO Barrio Salamanca
('eFISIO Barrio Salamanca', 'Physiotherapy', 'Premium English-speaking physiotherapy clinic in Madrid\'s prestigious Barrio Salamanca district. Part of the eFISIO network with 25+ licensed physiotherapists. Located on Calle Ruiz Perelló with convenient mezzanine level access. Specializes in manual therapy, sports physiotherapy, rehabilitative massage, dry needling, and pelvic floor rehabilitation. Offers cutting-edge treatments including shockwave therapy, EPTE percutaneous electrolysis, and ultrasound-guided interventions. Licensed by Colegio de Fisioterapeutas. Online booking with complimentary initial phone consultation.', 'Calle Ruiz Perelló, 3, Entreplanta', 'Madrid', 'Madrid', '+34 910 052 363', 'contacto@efisio.es', 'https://www.efisio.es/clinica/fisioterapia-barrio-salamanca/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

