('eFISIO Barrio del Pilar', 'Physiotherapy', 'Full-service English-speaking physiotherapy clinic in Madrid\'s Barrio del Pilar area. Part of the eFISIO network with 25+ licensed physiotherapists. Expert manual therapy, sports physiotherapy, post-traumatic rehabilitation, and neurological physiotherapy. Wide range of therapeutic massages including descontracturante, sports, relaxation, pregnancy, and leg fatigue treatments. Specialized services: dry needling, manual lymphatic drainage, pelvic floor therapy, and shockwave therapy. Licensed by Colegio de Fisioterapeutas. Online booking with complimentary initial phone consultation.', 'Calle Ginzo de Limia, 60', 'Madrid', 'Madrid', '+34 910 052 363', 'contacto@efisio.es', 'https://www.efisio.es/clinica/fisioterapia-barrio-del-pilar/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

